                    "text": "3. Written. For purposes of \u00a7 1002.14, an \u201cappraisal or other written valuation\u201d includes, without limitation, an appraisal or other valuation received or developed by the creditor in paper form (hard copy); electronically, such as CD or email; or by any other similar media. See \u00a7 1002.14(a)(5) regarding the provision of copies of appraisals and other written valuations to applicants via electronic means."
                }
            }
