                    "text": "4. Timing. Section 1002.14(a)(1) requires that the creditor \u201cprovide\u201d copies of appraisals and other written valuations to the applicant \u201cpromptly upon completion,\u201d or no later than three business days before consummation (for closed-end credit) or account opening (for open-end credit), whichever is earlier."
                }
            }
        ], 
        "1002-14-a-1-Interp-4-i": [
            {
                "action": "PUT", 
