                        "As discussed in the section-by-section analysis relating to \u00a7 1002.14(a)(5), the Bureau is updating the cross-reference in \u00a7 1002.4(d) to \u00a7 1002.14, to reflect that the new disclosure requirement is cited as \u00a7 1002.14(a)(2), rather than \u00a7 1002.14(a)(2)(i). This change will ensure that electronic disclosure standards in Regulation B apply to the new notice required by \u00a7 1002.14(a)(2) to the same extent as they have applied to the existing notice required by \u00a7 1002.14(a)(2)(i) that the new notice will replace."
